********************************************************************************
* 03 - Match GWP Regions to GADM Level-1
* Foubert, K. & Ruyssen, I. (2024) - JEMS
********************************************************************************
*
* Purpose: Maps Gallup World Poll region names to standardised GADM level-1 administrative units. Extensive manual harmonisation across 142 countries.
*
* Input:   GWP2016withGADM.dta
*
* Output:  GWP with harmonised GADM region identifiers
*
* Note: These scripts were developed as part of a collaborative research workflow
* between two co-authors over several years. Internal annotations, commented-out
* file paths, and exploratory code blocks reflect this iterative process and have
* been preserved for transparency and reproducibility.
********************************************************************************

* Cleaning GWP -> GADM codes

cls 
clear all 
set more off 
set scrollbufsize 500000 
set maxvar 10000
graph drop _all 
capture log close 

cd "D:\Dropbox\PhD Killian\Paper II\Data\GWP\Clean\dta\" // Fix computer Killian
*cd "C:\Users\kifouber\Dropbox\PhD Killian\Paper II\Data\GWP\Clean\dta\" // Laptop Killian
*cd "/Users/ilseruyssen/Dropbox/PhD Killian/Paper II/Data/GWP/Clean/dta"

use "GWP2016withGADM.dta"

gen regions=REGION_names
replace regions=REGION2_names if regions==""
